snippet.title: PS4『EARTH DEFENSE FORCE 4.1 WINGDIVER THE SHOOTER』PV
snippet.description:
Take to the skies with the elite Pale Team!

With combined sales of 850,000 of EARTH DEFENSE FORCE 4 and EARTH DEFENSE FORCE 4.1 THE SHADOW OF NEW DESPAIR comes the first spin off from the EDF series – a vertically scrolling shoot 'em up. 

Play for the first time as 'Pale Team' from the popular 'Wing Diver' division in a new story from THE SHADOW OF NEW DESPAIR. 

【Products】
PS4 Digital-Download Only 『EARTH DEFENSE FORCE 4.1 WINGDIVER THE SHOOTER』
Slated for Fall 2017
